risky business moves. Take the bill now and reap the benefits later.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Its a scary world out there especially for small business owners who think they can create the next Google by simply knowing a little HTML or hiring someone overseas for a fraction of the price. In my own personal experience, I have heard story upon story of completely unsatisfied customers who decide to outsource their web development and in the end waste their own time and money and have nothing to show for it. Don\'t be that person; heed my advice.</p>','3 Critical Problems for Internet Startups','','inherit','open','open','','232-revision-7','','','2010-09-15 20:17:26','2010-09-15 20:17:26','',232,'http://www.josephdickinson.com/232-revision-7/',0,'revision','',0),(248,1,'2010-09-15 20:17:27','2010-09-15 20:17:27','<div class=\"str\">1. <a href=\"http://www.androlib.com/android.application.com-rechild-advancedtaskkiller-jCEw.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">Task Killer</a></div>\r\n-  Have you ever entered task manager in Windows to kill awfully programmed programs? Its about time you download this application now, kill virtually any app on your android device.  Many developers aren\'t keeping your processor or your memory in mind when developing apps therefore leaving your android device mercilessly trying to run these inefficiently built programs. Its time you take charge!\r\n<div class=\"str\">2. <a href=\"http://www.appstorehq.com/startupauditor-android-174324/app\" target=\"_blank\">Startup Auditor</a></div>\r\n-  Another huge memory and processor hog with any computer system whether a mobile phone or computer alike is the startup processes. This application allows you to kill any start up process. However, I highly recommend spending the $.99 and get the full version to automatically kill any process on start up and keep it killed if it tries to relaunch (as many applications that are developed today do).\r\n<div class=\"str\">3. <a href=\"http://www.androidfreeware.net/download-timeriffic.html\" target=\"_blank\">Timeriffic</a></div> -  Another huge component to conserving battery on your Android Incredible phone is screen brightness, ringing volume, and more. With this app you choose at what time and what days you would like certain brightness levels and ringing volumes to increase or decrease. This not only saves you time in the long run from having to manually change all of these options, but it also is more accurate then having to slide a slider that is highly interactive. ','Best Apps to Save Battery for Android!','','inherit','open','open','','228-revision-4','','','2010-09-15 20:17:27','2010-09-15 20:17:27','',228,'http://www.josephdickinson.com/228-revision-4/',0,'revision','',0),(249,1,'2010-09-15 20:17:27','2010-09-15 20:17:27','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"/wp-content/images/nbooks.png\" alt=\"Why To Buy Netbook\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Many people think net-books are just not powerful enough for their demands. But, you maybe be enticed by their price-to-performance ratio. This especially should be your computer if you all do you is instant messaging, internet browsing, and other light-cpu tasks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"str\">1. Initial Cost</span> - Are you in the market for a new computer? How does $200 to $300 sound? This does not sacrifice what you can do however, you can just as easily connect to your facebook, or twitter, or stream Youtube videos.</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"str\">2. Option not with Windows</span> - For those of you (myself included) who absolutely loath Microsoft - you can now rejoice: some net books are offered with Windows 7 or a distribution of linux. In fact, most net books today can run both simultaneously (if you\'re that geeky).</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"str\">3. Easier Portability</span> - Did you know - some net books weight 1-2 lbs? This is a significant difference both when putting your net book in your laptop and when your carrying it around. Other primarily windows-based net books can weigh anywhere from 5 to 8 lbs.</p>\r\n\r\n','Three Reasons To Buy A Netbook','','inherit','open','open','','202-revision-7','','','2010-09-15 20:17:27','2010-09-15 20:17:27','',202,'http://www.josephdickinson.com/202-revision-7/',0,'revision','',0),(250,1,'2010-09-15 20:17:27','2010-09-15 20:17:27','<p>When looking to buy a computer the first thing you might see is a cheap dell for $500 and jump at it! But, you should reconsider, while a macbook can be a whopping $1000+ in the long run, the TCO (total cost of ownership) will be a lot less. I\'ll show you how:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"str\">1. Virtually no viruses</span> - While the mac operating system, may have a handful of viruses - the fact of the matter is : most people (to date) do not need antivirus. How does this save you? Well, consider you run a business and use your laptop to store information about clients and all of a sudden a virus steals all of the confidential customer data and sends them all hate mail while at the same thing steals all of the social security numbers and open accounts in them. Lesson learned: mac users typically would not have to worry about this.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"str\">2. Much faster</span> - The operating system behind a macbook is built behind the legendary: unix operating system. This increases not just your everyday browsing capabilities, but let\'s you develop software quicker, simultaneously run multiple applications, and on the off chance you need to leave your mac for the day; it will within seconds come and warmly welcome you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"str\">3. Native Backup Built In</span> - Time Machine! Every time you make an edit to something on your harddrive, Time Machine backs up that file immediately to an external drive (such as an External Hard drive, Flash Drive, etc). The best part of it is, if you want to backup to an earlier date, even years ago, you can with two clicks! Can you say no more losing your data?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"str\">4. Easier Program Install / Uninstall</span> - Simply drag and drop a program into the /applications/ directory on your mac and voila! You have installed a program. If you choose to then delete that file all you need to do is right click and \"Move to Trash\"; file deleted.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"str\">5. Longer Battery Life</span> - Have you ever been sitting in starbucks (or a local coffee shop) without your power cable and after 2 hours your computer is ready to die? Worry to longer, a macbook has 4-5 hours of battery life whether its idling or working between multiple programs; kiss good-bye those days where you need to furious save your work because your battery is going to die.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"str\">6. Need Windows? No Problem</span> - Have you thought about a windows program that you just can\'t get your hands off of? Well, you\'re in luck, by using Cross Over or Parallels or Mac\'s Native solution Boot Camp - you can natively run windows just like if you have a clunker PC to work on rejoice, you have the best of both worlds!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"str\">7. Develop out of the box</span> - No need to install all of this software when you first get it out of the box! Apple has done that for you, Apple preinstalls on its macbooks everything from Python to Php to AppleScript to C all editable in the native program X-Code (similiar to Visual Studio) - programmers : program from the get go!</p>\r\n<br /><br />\r\n<p>When all is said and done, the TCO for own a mac when you factor in time, money, and learning easily outbeats any PC-competitor. It runs like a champ out of the box. I\'ve owned both 3 different PC brands, 1 macbook, and 1 macbook pro. I cannot emphasive it enough; a mac comes out on top either way</p>','How a Macbook Will Knock Your Socks Off','','inherit','open','open','','209-revision-9','','','2010-09-15 20:17:27','2010-09-15 20:17:27','',209,'http://www.josephdickinson.com/209-revision-9/',0,'revision','',0),(